'''2-溴丙烷'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>7</sub>Br，是[[丙烷|丙烷]]的亚甲基氢被溴取代的产物。它的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]是[[1-溴丙烷|1-溴丙烷]]。

==制备==
2-溴丙烷可由[[丙烯|丙烯]]和[[溴化氢|溴化氢]]发生[[亲电加成反应|亲电加成反应]]得到：<ref>Griesbaum, Karl; Mach, Helmut. Crossover products from joint reactions of alkenes and alkynes with hydrogen halides. ''Chemische Berichte'', 1982. 115 (12): 3818-3829. ISSN: 0009-2940.</ref>
: [[File:Synthesis_isopropyl_bromide.svg|300px]]
[[异丙醇|异丙醇]]和溴化试剂（如[[硫酸|硫酸]]-[[溴化钠|溴化钠]]<ref>王玉凤, 王江. 2–溴丙烷合成的研究. 黑龙江日化, 1998, (4): 4-6.</ref>、[[磷|磷]]-[[溴|溴]]<ref>Goshorn, R. H.; Boyd, Thomas; Degering, E. F. Alkyl and alkylene bromides. II. Phosphorus and bromine method. ''Organic Syntheses'', 1941. 1 (2). 36-41. ISSN: 0078-6209.</ref>、[[三溴化磷|三溴化磷]]<ref>Mundy, Bradford P.; Stewart, Catherine A. Phosphorus(III) bromide. ''e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis'', 2008. pp 1-4. ISBN 978-0-470-84289-8.</ref>等）发生溴化反应，也能得到2-溴丙烷。

==反应==
2-溴丙烷可以用于合成异丙基化合物，例如在[[碳酸钾|碳酸钾]]的存在下，2-溴丙烷和[[4-羟基苯甲醛|4-羟基苯甲醛]]在[[乙腈|乙腈]]中反应，可以得到4-异丙氧基苯甲醛；<ref>Treu, Matthias. Synthesis of Novel Galanthamine Analog Acetylcholinesterase Inhibitors via Tandem Cyclization [Dissertation]. 2000. Vienna University of Technology.</ref>[[碳酸铯|碳酸铯]]作为碱、[[四(三苯基膦)钯|四(三苯基膦)钯]]作为催化剂，它和呋喃-2-硼酸反应，得到2-异丙基呋喃<ref>Li, Jiuyi; Lu, Lin; Pan, Qi; Ren, Yanwei; Liu, Bo; Yin, Biaolin. Palladium-​Catalyzed Dearomatizing Alkoxydiarylation of Furan Rings by Coupling with Arylboronic Acids: Access to Polysubstituted Oxabicyclic Compounds. ''Advanced Synthesis & Catalysis'', 2017. 359 (11): 2001-2007. ISSN: 1615-4150. DOI: 10.1002/adsc.201601437.</ref>。

它可以和[[碘化钠|碘化钠]]在[[丙酮|丙酮]]中发生卤素交换反应，生成[[2-碘丙烷|2-碘丙烷]]；<ref>Textbook of Practical Organic Chemistry, 5th Edition, Prentice Hall, 1989</ref>它和[[硫氰酸钠|硫氰酸钠]]发生类似反应，生成硫氰酸异丙酯。<ref>Shriner, R. L. Isopropyl thiocyanate. ''Organic Syntheses'', 1931. XI. 92-93. ISSN: 0078-6209. DOI: 10.15227/orgsyn.011.0092.</ref>它也可以和[[一氟化氯|一氟化氯]]反应，生成{{link-de|2-氟丙烷|2-Fluorpropan}}。<ref>Morozova, T. V.; Chuvatkin, N. N.; Panteleeva, I. Yu.; Boguslavskaya, L. S. Reactions of chlorine monofluoride. IV. Relative rates of the substitutive fluorination of bromo-substituted alkanes. Hydride and other migrations during fluorination. ''Zhurnal Organicheskoi Khimii'', 1984. 20 (7): 1379-1388. ISSN: 0514-7492.</ref>

